import axios from 'axios'; import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { useNavigate, useParams } from 'react-router-dom'; const Edit = () => { const {_id}=useParams(); const[values,setValues]=useState({uname:"",email:"",password:"",jobTitle:"",hireDate:Date,department:"",contact:"" }) useEffect(()=>{ const token=localStorage.getItem('user') axios.post(URI+"/userData",_id,{ Authorization:"Bearer "+token }) .then(res=>{ console.log("edit values",res) setValues(res.data) console.log(values) }).catch(err=>console.log("error occured")) },[] ) const URI="http://localhost:4000" const navigate=useNavigate() const changeHandler=(event)=>{ const {name,value}=event.target; setValues({...values,[name]:value}) } const submitHandler=(event)=>{ event.preventDefault(); console.log(values) axios.post(URI + "/update",values) .then(res=>{ console.log("dbres", res) navigate("/profile/Employee") }) .catch(error=>console.error(error.message)) } return (
